data.answer: This picture gives information about two girls and a crocodile toy. As we can see from the picture, two girls are laughing in the picture. Their mouths are open, and they look pretty happy. The girl on the left of the picture has long curled yellow hair and white skin. She is wearing a silver necklace and a blue and black shirt. She is about twenty years old, and she has a red face. She is imitating the dinosaur with her mouth open. She looks thrilled and energic. The girl on the right side of the picture is laughing as well. As we can see from the picture, she is holding a crocodile toy in her left hand and wearing a purple sweater. She is pretty young and excited. I guess she is around 20 years old. The crocodile toy is green, and it is a famous toy called crocodile dentists. The classic Crocodile Dentist Game is a super fun and easy-to-learn game. Play a solo round of crocodile dentists or gather with up to four friends for a fun game. With no assembly required, this game is quick and easy to set up, so your little ones can get right to playing. This portable game is easy to bring along on road trips or visits to friends or grandparents. （219 字）
